            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Providentissimo <lb n="2"/>principi rectori <lb n="3"/>orbis ac domino <lb n="4"/>fundatori pacis <lb n="5"/>aeternae <lb n="6"/>Diocletiano <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>invicto <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifici</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ger</abbr><ex>manico</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Pers</abbr><ex>ico</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> VII <lb n="10"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> IIII patri <expan><abbr>pat</abbr><ex>riae</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/>proco<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sept</abbr><ex>imius</ex></expan> <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost">Val</supplied>entio <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>raeses</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>rovinciae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>aetiae</ex></expan> <lb n="13"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>evotus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>umini</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>aiestatique</ex></expan> eiusdem
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Stark bestoßen, Inschrift stellenweise schwer lesbar. In Z. 6 Am Zeilenende möglicherweise noch ein zweites, irrtümlich eingehauenes P. In Z. 13 links noch die oberen Ansätze der Buchstaben zu erkennen.</p>
            </div>
